{
  "stem": "3721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one morning, I decided that we had to go put my uniform on and go look what's happening.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the meantime, I stuck my head out from the Swiss Schutz House, where I stayed in the basement, and I see the Russian soldiers walking around.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [CRYING] so happened again, is I started going-- I went down, yelling, hey, the Russians are here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, the Russians were not that interested in Jews or non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were also-- they, they-- guns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I thought-- I knew the two words he yelled at me-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, well, I don't give a shit whether you're-- you'll excuse the expression-- whether you're Jewish or not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They just kept on going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These are the front troops.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were the first guard that came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were unbelievable collection of, of riffraff with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- but they did the fighting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And, of course, that day, I went down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I brought everybody up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then I told them that first thing I want to do is go home to see if there are any remnants of my family.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was leaving Budapest, like, two days after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I remember, for the first two days, I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Not only that, I found out that some of the men from my hometown who were older than me-- they were in the labor camps-- were captured by the Russians, and that they joined the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So quite a few of them were in the main troops that took in-- they were in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I met one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
